These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, fanta, iced-tea, juice, lemonade, water
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, blues, classical, disco, folk, house, salsa
House: wooden, townhouse, futuristic, tower, victorian, gothic-revival, cottage
The people have 7 different hobbies: writing, fishing, sudoku, hiking, board-games, traveling, filmmaking
 1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking water##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the right of the wooden house##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is the victorian house##1
 4. the victorian house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
 5. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the fan of house##1
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 8. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 9. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
10. the fan of classical is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
12. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
13. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
14. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
15. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
16. the victorian house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
17. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
18. the fan of classical is on the right of the tower house##1
19. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in the middle##1
20. the tower house is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
21. the fan of blues is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |    5     |     6      |       7       |
| Beverage      | fanta    | 7up     | water  | lemonade   | iced-tea | juice      | cola          |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | disco   | house  | folk       | ambient  | blues      | classical     |
| House         | wooden | townhouse | victorian | gothic-revival | futuristic   | tower     | cottage |
| Hobby     | filmmaking      | traveling   | writing   | sudoku  | hiking  | board-games | fishing       |

